      "title": "Sri Lanka: Aragalaya activist arrested aboard flight to Dubai",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st);\u00a0 The Criminal Investigations Department carried out an inflight arrest of an Aragalaya Activist today.",
        "The CID arrested an Aragalaya Activist identified as \u2018Danish Ali\u2019 while he was attempting to travel to Dubai.",
        "Social Media footage showed the infight arrest, and Police said he was connected to the incident where activists stormed into the Sri Lanka Rupavahini Corporation recently.",
        "CID arrested an individual named \u2018Danish Ali\u2019 when attempting to travel to Dubai. He was arrested inside a flight, and was connected to storming into the Sri Lanka Rupavahini Corporation \u2013 Police#lka #SriLanka #SLnews #News1st #ProtestLK #SriLankaProtest #CID #Arrest #Inflight pic.twitter.com/28RYL6FPTI",
        "Five COVID deaths for Monday (25), over 100 cases today (26)"
